HEADWORD: Skyey
<hw>Sky"ey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like the sky; ethereal;
being in the sky.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Skyey</xex> regions.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Thackeray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Sublime on the towers of my <qex>skyey</qex> bowers,⟦br⟧
Lightning, my pilot, sits.</q> <rj><qau>Shelley.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sky-high</ent>⟦br⟧
